HEADWORD: Ancillary administration
<hw>An"cil*la*ry ad*min`is*tra"tion</hw>. <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>An
administration subordinate to, and in aid of, the primary or principal
administration of an estate.</def>⟦br⟧
